COMPILE:
    python setup.py build

JERASURE LIBRARY:
    galois.c
    galois.h
    jerasure.c
    jerasure.h
    jerasure.pxd  --> needed by cython

CAUCHY REED-SOLOMON CODE:
    cauchyec.pyx --> cython code

GALOIS BUFFER
    galoisbuffer.pyx --> Filed operations in the buffer.

CODING/DECODING TEST:
    print.py --> Simple verbose example
    test.py --> Performance eval example for different w values.
